<div id="attachment_35759" style="width: 610px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://www.ikexue.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/科技快讯20150910附图.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-35759" src="http://www.ikexue.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/科技快讯20150910附图.jpg" alt="图为桃儿七的植株和果实，图片引自原报道" width="600" height="338" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">图为桃儿七的植株和果实，图片引自原报道</p></div>
