<div id="attachment_35696" style="width: 610px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://www.ikexue.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/09-08-15.jpg" class="cboxElement" rel="example_group"35694><img class="size-full wp-image-35696" src="http://www.ikexue.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/09-08-15.jpg" alt="授予拉斯克奖得主的雕像（图片来源http://www.hopkinsmedicine.org/about/history/timeline/)" width="600" height="404" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">授予拉斯克奖得主的雕像（图片来源http://www.hopkinsmedicine.org/about/history/timeline/)</p></div>
